# Momora Core

Read `AGENTS.md` and `docs/TECH_SPEC.md` before non-trivial changes.

## MVP scope

In scope: auth, family profiles, plain-text + voice memories, AI portraits/illustrations, timeline/calendar/search, daily reminders.

Out of scope: monetization, data export, SSO, photo-upload illustrations, family sharing, pets.

## Stack (fixed)

Expo SDK 56 · Expo Router · TanStack Query · Supabase · `expo-audio` · EAS dev client.

Do not introduce Redux, `expo-av`, or Expo Go assumptions.

## Non-negotiables

- Memory **text saves before** AI runs; illustration failure never blocks save.
- Max **4 tags** per memory (UI + backend).
- **RLS** on all user data; **signed URLs** for private images.
- **No secrets in git** — `.env*`, API keys, keystores are gitignored; use `.env.example` only.
- **No OpenAI/service keys** in client or `EXPO_PUBLIC_*`.
- **Voice audio not stored** — only transcribed text.
- **Minimal diffs** — no drive-by refactors.

## Schema/API changes

Migration + regenerate `src/types/database.ts` + update `docs/TECH_SPEC.md` in same change.

## Feature docs

Major features require `docs/features/<name>.md` in the same PR. Read existing feature docs before extending.

## Testing

Major features require **unit + integration** tests in the same PR; **e2e** for user-facing flows. See `docs/TESTING.md`.
